/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/08\/05\/clean-mouth-teeth-pleasing\/","url_meta":{"origin":33110,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Siwak: Clean mouth and teeth pleasing to the Lord","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 5, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Umar reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cYou must use the toothstick, as it is pleasant for the mouth and pleasing to the Lord.\u201d Source: Musnad Ah\u0323mad 5865 Source: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Arna'ut \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0639\u064f\u0645\u064e\u0631\u064e \u0623\u064e\u0646\u0651\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0646\u0651\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a\u0651\u064e \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0645\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0643\u064f\u0645\u0652\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33100,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/08\/05\/using-miswak-every-ablution\/","url_meta":{"origin":33110,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Siwak: Using Miswak with every ablution","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 5, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Umm Habibah reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWere it not hardship for my nation, I would have commanded them to use the toothstick with every prayer as they perform ablution.\u201d Source: Musnad Ah\u0323mad 26763 Grade: Sahih li ghayrihi (authentic due to external evidence)\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":25593,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2017\/12\/10\/easy-ummah-siwak-wudu\/","url_meta":{"origin":33110,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Ease: The Prophet makes things easy for his nation","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 10, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWere it not hardship upon my nation, I would have commanded them to perform ablution with every prayer or to use the toothstick with every ablution. And I would have delayed the evening prayer until a\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":25645,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2017\/12\/19\/gabriel-you-are-unkempt\/","url_meta":{"origin":33110,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Gabriel: Angel avoid visiting the unkempt","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 19, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Abbas reported: It was said to the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, Gabriel, upon him be peace, has been slow to come to you.\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cAnd why should he not be slow to come to me while you are around me\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":26498,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2018\/06\/10\/iman-before-quran\/","url_meta":{"origin":33110,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Quran: Faith is given to a Muslim before Quran","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 10, 2018","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Amr reported: A man came to the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, and he said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, I recite the Quran but I do not find that my heart understands it.\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cVerily, your heart is filled with faith, and\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33116,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/08\/05\/clean-mouth-for-angels-quran\/","url_meta":{"origin":33110,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Siwak: Clean your mouth for the angels, the Quran","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 5, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Ali reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, when the servant uses the toothstick and then stands to pray, an angel stands behind him and listens to his recitation. The angel draws near until his mouth coincides with his and nothing of the Quran comes out\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/33110","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/daily